{"tid":2298734,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今次第4波好快會回落（分析）","createTime":"2020-11-24T09:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T10:32:49.000Z","uid":308491,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc3ed5ae081d5aba6c14fae18aa4858069484f8","tid":2298734,"uid":308491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:02:30.000Z","msg":"前幾次比左經驗政府去處理（雖然最主要既原因：關口都係冇封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n同埋依家多左檢測中心比人測有冇中招，d人捉得好快，所以今次先冇爆到好似上次第3波禁，上到100宗，應該會開始回落<br />\n<br />\n估計：12月頭或者12月10號左右會回落番去10月左右既確診情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ac8ade7544f11ea81ec28a6f441af698f57a5a","tid":2298734,"uid":303119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"留名binc"},{"pid":"0cbebc8bf5b53d6bfbd6fe191ed3b7e0040c0a29","tid":2298734,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928c0893919ee264ba654fcb8056f18981c98a24","tid":2298734,"uid":162380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27adbe8c3c84c24e1069a8eb5ba020bcb89bc71","tid":2298734,"uid":276839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"會有第5，6，7，8，9.........波。"},{"pid":"fcb8277816b4b3ca6bbe5aba63d859c88fac8716","tid":2298734,"uid":181258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"樓主帶啲風向想話政府抗疫成功有效？<br />\n咁就係分析？學下台灣先啦"},{"pid":"d2b96dbc890623ac2c1073241a8cf324a53ffec1","tid":2298734,"uid":308491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcb8277816b4b3ca6bbe5aba63d859c88fac8716","tid":2298734,"uid":181258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"reply